{"type": "article", "id": 28430, "title": "阿玛尼推出运动胶囊系列，Alexander McQueen 行李箱来一个？｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-20T11:15:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 10368, "name": "功能性"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 2381, "name": "行李箱"}, {"id": 6350, "name": "骷髅"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 11493, "name": "Fragment Design"}, {"id": 29173, "name": "NMG"}, {"id": 12792, "name": "Neiman Marcus"}, {"id": 3113, "name": "Salvatore Ferragamo"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 3081, "name": "Emporio Armani"}, {"id": 29174, "name": "Antonia"}, {"id": 16575, "name": "Globe-Trotter"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}, {"id": 17471, "name": "Selena Gomez"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171627Amu3CRJdjqDLczXb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/neiman-marcus-rough-times-expenses-payroll-10461723/\"><b>美国高端百货集团 NMG 可能出售</b></a>｜运营高端百货 Neiman Marcus、Bergdorf Goodman 的 Neiman Marcus 集团可能出售，据传 NMG 首席执政官兼总裁 Karen Katz 正在中国寻求潜在买家。关于这一消息目前众说纷纭，但 Neiman 确实处于水深火热之中，上季度净收益从去年同期的 1980 万美元下跌至 380 万美元，总收入也从 12.2 亿美元跌至 11.7 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Italy-s-Ferragamo-CEO-sees-no-let-up-in-luxury-sector-slowdown,705155.html\"><b>菲拉格慕一季度核心利润胜预期</b></a>｜意大利品牌 Salvatore Ferragamo 一季度核心利润上涨了 5%，超出预期，但收入下跌了 2% 至 3.21 亿欧元。考虑到奢侈品市场整体的增速放缓，行政长官 Michele Norsa 在品牌的米兰男装周走秀发布前表示奢侈部门将集中于风险管理，相对于推动销售来说更关注扩大产品的利润空间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/louis-vuitton-fragment-design-collaboration#\"><b>Louis Vuitton 将与藤原浩的品牌推出联名</b></a>｜男装创意总监 Kim Jones 日前宣布与藤原浩创办的品牌 fragment design 推出合作系列。这个混合奢侈品及街头时尚的联名系列将在藤原浩的 THE PARK • ING GINZA 新概念店里售卖。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/vogue-mexico-karla-martinez-editor-in-chief-10459838/\"><b>墨西哥版 <i>Vogue</i> 任命新主编</b></a>｜墨西哥及拉丁美洲<i> Vogue </i>近日任命 Karla Martinez 为主编，接替 Kelly Talamas，后者将担任创意总监。这一变动进出现在 Karla 以副主编身份加入一个月之后。38 岁的 Karla 过去在美版 <i>Vogue</i>、纽约时报的 <i>T Magazine</i>、<i>W Magazine </i>等杂志担任过时尚编辑及总监职位。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/jil-sander-2017-spring-collection\">Jil Sander  发布 2017 春季系列男装</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171613CEm6Q0K5sNAYfc9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171614fKvnetFk0o7TdA8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171614lBdYTQ8iv2aF0s7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171615EoyMkhjNbpIz5UL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171615uQ8kBX7jOH1fmWMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Emporio Armani 与米兰多时尚精品店 Antonia 合作，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/emporio-armani-teams-up-with-antonia-for-an-ultra-functional-2016-spring-summer-collection\">推出 2016 春夏的胶囊系列</a>，强调功能性。系列中还包括与米兰理工大学合作的电镀刚自行车。6 月 19 日将在米兰 Excelsior 酒店推出预览，9 月在 Emporio Armani 特选门店上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171616C96XHMpbPwJUY0r7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171616nUdpP92Qkr7Ne1AW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171616ujgCYwP0zUrSZGRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021716170kFD4VZ9tvcwSxfr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021716170yu7QzXOIKUMphms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171618FV8RnwWCjYTfX6kI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/17/11964718/selena-gomez-louis-vuitton-campaign\">Selena Gomez 为 Louis Vuitton 拍摄了秋冬季大片</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171618RXxh23gKfeE4Z7Aa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171619EJrvm1gdw03spNt7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/salvatore-ferragamo-mens-spring-10461016/#!38/salvatore-ferragamo-mens-spring-2017-38/\">Salvatore Ferragamo 2017 春夏男装系列不错</a>： </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171619eGmixs7vgPLcfoAD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171620nuRhfS2BwLKVzvTm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171620P9bsQD0tF3gHaeZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171621sVknpeIDB1SXKOGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171621DyF8z7jLaNYXCiq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171622xbq2ED0iR8juBe4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">英国品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/globe-trotter-alexander-mcqueen-bags\"> Alexander McQueen  与 Globe-Trotter  合作</a>，推出两个尺寸的行李箱。标志性的骷髅形状，出现在外部的挂锁和内部的印花，价格在 1200-2815 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021716220yjt2DSxRmi1avc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171623c9tWuCKyd1rj4bgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171624yCWsAfNcOXEiQuD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Raf Simons 发布 2016 秋冬季大片：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171624kTvJ6StMyF4hbIpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171625yjzhLWMKG0VxFSJm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021716259aRnskmDz1VHTA4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171625KYh9rBZ5jikzWS0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}